Reasoning: The paper deals with wireless communication systems and the mitigation of the effects of fading, which are topics typically studied in the Information Theory (cs.IT), Communications (cs.COMM), and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The use of pilot symbols and adaptive schemes also suggests a focus on Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI). Finally, the use of binary signaling and the analysis of autocorrelation suggest a possible connection to Multimedia (cs.MM).
